          "contentHtml": "<p>I can’t argue with you about the fact that he was an extremely privileged person nor that I could rule out that he could possibly be playing with the configuration of his body for attention and money. What I do know is that he has given a lot of attention to the LGBTQIA community even if he did not intend to do so, which I think creates an entirely separate debate about giving other human beings their undeniable rights. One of the only things that I hope people take away from all of this is that respecting other people as well as their opinions brings a lot more peace to the world even if they don’t agree with anything they say, which is what I’m ultimately hoping to do: spread this ideology. Forcing someone to change their train of thought is probably one of the hardest things to do if it’s not impossible. With a little more respect for each other and the things that we do, maybe the world will be a better place.</p>",
